  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/be7dc67c8daf20e7636f74e0adc053d7.avif?t=1685592204\" width=616 height=198 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/f6e37bf23399731e4f6a7e415c0f3426.webp?t=1685592204\" width=616 height=17 /></span><br><strong>Touch Down & Sprial Up!</strong><br><br>An agonizingly difficult 2D Platformer that can be played by using only one hand, or two fingers to be more precise!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/7a5f405e8dd1cead50a61496b8e77308.poster.avif?t=1685592204\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/7a5f405e8dd1cead50a61496b8e77308.webm?t=1685592204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/7a5f405e8dd1cead50a61496b8e77308.mp4?t=1685592204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>When on the ground, use Left-Mouse-Button to charge up your Spring<br><br>When in the air, move your mouse to rotate your body<br><br>And leave the rest to the in-game physics<br><br>Oh, and when at the point of giving up, try using your knowledge of in-game physics and your strategic thinking to figure out the route forward. Good Luck!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/0f597ef8ae45e46e94197fb17a4db472.poster.avif?t=1685592204\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/0f597ef8ae45e46e94197fb17a4db472.webm?t=1685592204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/0f597ef8ae45e46e94197fb17a4db472.mp4?t=1685592204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/f6e37bf23399731e4f6a7e415c0f3426.webp?t=1685592204\" width=616 height=17 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/be7dc67c8daf20e7636f74e0adc053d7.avif?t=1685592204\" width=616 height=198 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/f6e37bf23399731e4f6a7e415c0f3426.webp?t=1685592204\" width=616 height=17 /></span><br><strong>Touch Down & Sprial Up!</strong><br><br>An agonizingly difficult 2D Platformer that can be played by using only one hand, or two fingers to be more precise!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/7a5f405e8dd1cead50a61496b8e77308.poster.avif?t=1685592204\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/7a5f405e8dd1cead50a61496b8e77308.webm?t=1685592204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/7a5f405e8dd1cead50a61496b8e77308.mp4?t=1685592204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>When on the ground, use Left-Mouse-Button to charge up your Spring<br><br>When in the air, move your mouse to rotate your body<br><br>And leave the rest to the in-game physics<br><br>Oh, and when at the point of giving up, try using your knowledge of in-game physics and your strategic thinking to figure out the route forward. Good Luck!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/0f597ef8ae45e46e94197fb17a4db472.poster.avif?t=1685592204\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/0f597ef8ae45e46e94197fb17a4db472.webm?t=1685592204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/0f597ef8ae45e46e94197fb17a4db472.mp4?t=1685592204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395730/extras/f6e37bf23399731e4f6a7e415c0f3426.webp?t=1685592204\" width=616 height=17 /></span>",
